narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would because I think research has many applications.

I'm so happy we were given the opportunity to do a senior project this year. I appreciated the flexibility in the program. I learned really useful skills and research concepts that I wasn't able to gain at other points in my engineering education.

It is the Senior Project, so by nature of the class, it is whatever you make of it! I have heard that the other ENVE senior class option is also pretty laid back, but I would still recommend the project. That being said, start it early! Because no matter how long you think it is going to take, it will always take twice as long.
